{"tid":508463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：即將公布重開公民廣場","createTime":"2017-12-24T09:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T03:12:03.000Z","uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5eee3d88c333e41f344461dcedd88446d0719f1f","tid":508463,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/174056_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F174056_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=effe465e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n署理行政長官張建宗表示，將在本周公布重開公民廣場（名政府總部東翼前地）安排，現時正斟酌最後細節，料會回復至2014年的環境，即晚上11時後要持有證件才可使用通道，張建宗指，有關舉措顯示政府包容開放，加強溝通。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，侍產假由3天加至5天的建議，有信心2018年可以落實，認為由於大家有共識，亦得到僱主也認同，故相對簡單。至於增加產假，政府亦認同是時候全面檢討，亦願意作出承擔，扮演積極角色，至於承擔程度仍然開放。<br />\n<br />\n對於強積金對沖的新建議，張建宗形容是政府大突破，將在一段長過渡期內補貼僱主，讓他們應付取消對沖的即時影響，但政府不能夠永遠承擔，故會有一個期限性。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，通過修改議事規則之後，政府將會恢復向立法會提交草案，如早前抽起的印花稅修訂草案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/張建宗-將公布重開公民廣場-顯政府包容開放/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E5%B0%87%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4-%E9%A1%AF%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%8C%85%E5%AE%B9%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%2F&d=itbyeSTope6mGZ4l99DsLROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1cc0c1d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E5%B0%87%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4-%E9%A1%AF%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%8C%85%E5%AE%B9%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%2F&h=4125be45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/張建宗-將公布重開公民廣場-顯政府包容開放/</a>"},{"pid":"2617912f9f62cbc13cac1a7245f945b8d8068113","tid":508463,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"販民：政府願意重開公民廣場，代表有誠意。<br />\n           我哋都要表達誠意，通過國歌法<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b84dd7a21ef34b98362fdaab4609712fbebeac","tid":508463,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc48b0c4d0b6c139baff6dd44d4e436e55e87ec","tid":508463,"uid":130247,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"47e7dfe8fedea2a264f20bf9f78fd665e6e1a3e0","tid":508463,"uid":87780,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:14:55.000Z","msg":"又嚟一啖砂糖一啖屎臬策略<br />\n得政治智慧係BB level 既飯民先會落搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3f7d932ca46249e028a2ba8af7b54b7abd4119","tid":508463,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb5ecb0120b9de04b58e9243496bc4d4b97d3d7","tid":508463,"uid":150720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"所謂勇武個班人坐緊監先至重開公民廣場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5597c3cd896d3cef0d2d9b778f0dc7f62d056fb4","tid":508463,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47e7dfe8fedea2a264f20bf9f78fd665e6e1a3e0","tid":508463,"uid":87780,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:14:55.000Z","msg":"又嚟一啖砂糖一啖屎臬策略<br />\n得政治智慧係BB level 既飯民先會落搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:12:14.000Z","msg":"砂糖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個野本來就開放，封鳩完開返算咩砂糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泛民就會咩歡迎改善乜乜關係云云，之後311叫人投佢<img src=\"/assets/f